  meanings
    entry
      definitions
        entry
          definition "(of words or symbols) The entity, perception, feeling or concept thereby represented or evoked."
        entry
          definition "The value, purpose, importance, point or significance (of something beyond the fact of that thing's existence)."
          example "the meaning of life"
        entry
          definition "The object or concept that a word or phrase denotes, or that which a sentence says."
        entry
          definition Intention.
      partOfSpeech noun
      synonyms (sense definition)
  phonetic "/ˈmiːnɪŋ/"
